0.2 () - Doom Town / Wipers
---------------------------

This release will wipe out your conf !

General
 * Handle configuration with GSettings. #22
 * Emit notifications with GNotification. #22
 * Load/store station list with GMarkup. #22

Fixes
 * Fix desktop filename in mpris2 backend. #26

Translations
 * Goodvibes is now translated with the web-based translation service Weblate.

Dependencies
 * Drop compile-time libnotify.
 * Drop compile-time libxml2.
 * Add run-time dconf-gsettings-backend.



